{"tid":1561334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同我推到有記者朋友睇到---\"一群有良心的香港人\"","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T15:02:39.000Z","uid":180553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dac846682ed2f5cd3647c47e8c76dcc0c5fcf59e","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"好多時新聞都話示威者係&quot;年輕人&quot;<br />\n咁咪比錯覺覺得示威係搞事囉，特別係d 廢老<br />\n但大家都知，依家出黎行既示威者年齡層好闊<br />\n我覺得應該尊重返其他年齡層人士，亦要比全香港，全世界知香港示威者唔只係得&quot;年輕人&quot;<br />\n<br />\n大家比d idea 記得改改個名<br />\n <br />\n&quot;一群有良心的香港人&quot; 取代&quot;年輕人&quot;<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n#光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"a83f8ae58362fa23a36b2e0584b5b5b2c68bd736","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"一群有良心的香港人"},{"pid":"244450b89afe3859baff111ded88fb21b3ad745b","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"一群有良心的香港人"},{"pid":"bf2a5d781cc6335dfd352aa04d8d9efee3ffd81e","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8c56385c188996bc83053f855ed6ac067d45e38","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"大家比下意見"},{"pid":"b5e338a9a889447d47f993eb1ab5fd54ba16f9c6","tid":1561334,"uid":180553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cce7b0729877da51e74abfc672dfd3f4d05a5ea","tid":1561334,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:26:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: